## 🎯 What is SecureHire?

SecureHire is a **dual-mode interview & meeting platform** that combines:

- ⚡ **WebRTC-based** peer-to-peer real-time communication
- 🤖 **AI-powered proctoring** with behavioral & visual analysis
- 📊 **Live dashboards** with risk scoring and violation logs

Whether you're a recruiter running secure 1:1 interviews or hosting scalable group meetings — SecureHire has you covered.

---

## ✨ Features

### 🧑‍💻 Interview Mode (1:1)

#### 🔹 Normal Mode
- Real-time video & audio via WebRTC
- Low-latency peer-to-peer communication
- End-to-end encrypted sessions

#### 🔹 Advanced Mode ⚡ — AI Proctoring
> Fully customizable — enable/disable each feature individually

| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| 👁️ Eye Tracking | Detects gaze deviation from screen |
| 🧑‍🤝‍🧑 Multi-Face Detection | Alerts when multiple faces appear |
| 🎤 Voice Detection | Flags background speech or coaching |
| 🖥️ Tab Switch Detection | Detects candidate leaving the session tab |
| 📋 Copy-Paste Detection | Monitors clipboard activity |
| 📊 Behavior Analysis | Aggregated risk scoring & activity timeline |

---

### 👥 Meeting Mode (1:Many)
- Group video conferencing with multiple participants
- In-session text chat & participant management
- SFU-ready architecture for horizontal scaling (mediasoup)

---

### 🔑 Code-Based Joining System

Every session generates a **unique 6-character alphanumeric code**. Candidates can join via:

- Entering the code directly
- Clicking a shareable link

```
https://securehire.app/join/A1B2C3
```

---

### 📊 Smart Monitoring Dashboard

- 🎥 Live video feeds of all candidates
- 🚨 Real-time alerts per violation type
- 📈 Per-candidate risk score (0–100)
- 📝 Timestamped violation logs
- 🔔 Configurable alert thresholds

---

## 🧠 System Architecture

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                  Landing Page                   │
└───────────────────────┬─────────────────────────┘
                        │
               Authentication (JWT / Google OAuth)
                        │
              ┌─────────▼──────────┐
              │     Dashboard      │
              └──────┬──────┬──────┘
                     │      │
              ┌──────▼──┐ ┌─▼───────┐
              │  Create  │ │  Join   │
              └──────┬───┘ └───┬─────┘
                     │         │
              Select Mode   Enter Code
                     │         │
              Generate Code Join Room
                     │
        ┌────────────▼──────────────────┐
        │   Session (WebRTC + Signaling) │
        │                               │
        │  ┌────────────────────────┐   │
        │  │   AI Proctoring Engine │   │
        │  │  face-api.js / OpenCV  │   │
        │  └────────────────────────┘   │
        │                               │
        │  ┌────────────────────────┐   │
        │  │   Monitoring Dashboard  │   │
        │  │   Alerts / Risk Score  │   │
        │  └────────────────────────┘   │
        └───────────────────────────────┘
```

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| **Frontend** | React (Vite), Tailwind CSS, Axios, React Router |
| **Backend** | Django, Django REST Framework, Django Channels |
| **Real-Time** | WebRTC (P2P), mediasoup SFU (optional) |
| **AI / Detection** | face-api.js, OpenCV.js, TensorFlow.js |
| **Database** | MongoDB |
| **Cache & Messaging** | Redis |
| **Auth** | JWT + Google OAuth 2.0 |
| **Deployment** | Vercel (Frontend) · Render / AWS (Backend) |

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
securehire/
│
├── frontend/
│   ├── pages/            # Route-level page components
│   ├── components/       # Reusable UI components
│   ├── webrtc/           # WebRTC connection logic
│   └── hooks/            # Custom React hooks
│
└── backend/
    ├── apps/             # Django apps (users, sessions, alerts)
    ├── api/              # REST API endpoints
    ├── signaling/        # WebSocket signaling server
    └── models/           # MongoDB models / schemas
```

